        "html": "<p>Experienced <strong>DevOps Engineer</strong> with 6+ years specializing in cloud infrastructure, automation, and CI/CD pipelines. Expert in AWS, Kubernetes, and Infrastructure as Code with a track record of improving deployment frequency by 10x and reducing infrastructure costs by 40%. Passionate about reliability engineering, observability, and building self-healing systems that scale.</p>"
